sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant CF as Cloudflare edge
    participant Tunnel as Cloudflare Tunnel
    participant Envoy as Envoy Gateway
    participant Echo as echo service

    Browser->>CF: GET https://echo.wcygan.net/
    CF->>Tunnel: Forward over tunnel
    Tunnel->>Envoy: HTTP request
    Envoy->>Echo: Route by Host header
    Echo-->>Envoy: JSON echo response
    Envoy-->>Tunnel: 200 OK
    Tunnel-->>CF: Response
    CF-->>Browser: JSON + cf-ray
